schools.name: J. M. Tate Senior High School

data.description: Price Improvement! Spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath home on a half over lot with plenty of privacy. This home provides a country feel but still close to shopping, restaurants, schools and more! Great room offers plenty of space to gather, wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceilings. Off of the Florida room is an above ground pool with deck to enjoy those summer days. Master bedroom has bay windows and sitting area/office and walk-in closet. Roof was replaced in 2022 and HVAC was replaced 6 months ago.
